#: /home/nils/src/docs/system-config-date-docs/doc/C/system-config-date-complete.xml:73(para)
msgid "From the desktop, go to <menuchoice><guimenu>the main menu on the panel (the menu with the \"f\" icon)</guimenu><guisubmenu>System</guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Administration</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Date &amp; Time</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"
